{"tid":1694592,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"已經有第一位手足因警暴而係大家面前離去，肯將怒火用於行動上未？","createTime":"2019-11-05T08:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T09:09:33.000Z","uid":34355,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b379665d5de6c40f14b6aa572e91960bbb38212c","tid":1694592,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:23:25.000Z","msg":"接近5個月<br />\n跳樓  <br />\n831  <br />\n被自殺<br />\n<br />\n當時你可以呃自己無證據所以我地鋤班狗唔入<br />\n<br />\n但係宜家呢？警暴嘅行為已經透過科大手足向各大傳媒公告天下。<br />\n<br />\n我屌晒你班呃自己嘅老母，你地無面具嘅同我戴個口罩full black bloc 上街，今日之後真係無藉口再快樂抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭根本唔需要冷氣軍師係連登做即時討論，多位手足落場總比一個keyboard fighter好<br />\n<br />\n今晚發夢齊齊九西見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5616f0cde7dcbd977af7520f80535df5a40b7c3","tid":1694592,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:27:50.000Z","msg":"今晚曱甴平都會戴面具上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27396d4cb0edcea4816e5b316bf7209ab9da53b6","tid":1694592,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"今晚出黎  我要全部人!!"},{"pid":"247d4149233337460339a4c6fcc88568c6caac33","tid":1694592,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:30:30.000Z","msg":"三毛沖入來撲火,遂隻block"},{"pid":"0b75c841394bb4eadb418258fb141fb10650ca3c","tid":1694592,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"戴口罩 戴面具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffaa0d1af77fb4b4be3feb53fbf4c5988879d13","tid":1694592,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"今晚開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324ba2ce0dbac60386aea610db8192e3cf32cb3e","tid":1694592,"uid":649